What's up guys!

So here's what we know. Facebook does not like me, or this page. The most recent 30 day ban was absolutely ridiculous especially since they blocked my chat functions too. It was for the dishwasher pants pic which had literally nothing in it that goes against their terms of service or "community guidelines". To further prove this, someone sent me a screenshot of them reporting the same exact picture posted by several other pages only to be told that it does not violate their community guidelines so nothing would be done. It's basically gotten to a point where I have no idea what I can and can't post on this page anymore if I can get banned for things that they tell others don't violate their terms. The inconsistencies they show are insane since I have seen videos of nudity and gore that somehow stay. Last week I saw a video of a dude biting the head off a mouse and it was shared about 100k times, and the week before someone who jumped off a building and splat at the bottom. Neither of which have been removed. It's safe to say that there are some very weird double standards at work. I really don't know what to do at this point. I could continue posting stuff that is somewhat edgy, but if I can get banned for things they say are not against their terms, i'm sort of at a standstill. 

The page could always be remade, and started fresh from a new account since apparently your past bans give you a zero tolerance policy on anything. Instagram is also another option if you guys would rather we start fresh from there. Would love to hear your thoughts and opinions on what to do next.

Thanks guys

- I Feel It

30 day ban felt like an eternity... Anyways I feel like it's time to just clear some stuff up. It's getting really lame that I've been accused by several people of running a hate group which is not what this is about.. I am a very accepting, tolerant person and do not and will not post in spite of anyone's race, gender, sexual orientation, or religion. If you haven't noticed yet, I just post whatever I find funny, which can sometimes be regarded as offensive. If that's the kind of humor you don't like, then simply don't look at the page. I'm not sure why this is so difficult for some people to grasp. No one is forcing you to stay on it just to make sure you are offended. Stop taking every little thing so seriously and ruining it for the people who actually have a sense of humor. Laugh a little, it feels better than being pissed. Additionally, if anyone's getting personally attacked on the page which I hope doesn't happen, reach out to me and we'll find a solution. I don't want anyone to have a bad time. Let's continue to feel it. Have a great weekend everyone!
